{"tid":1113321,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"［集體回憶］一人一首鄭秀文好聽既歌","createTime":"2019-04-17T23:58:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T03:52:59.000Z","uid":17809,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"58daf59a9ceed2b33e224ca69928a50fa94d7949","tid":1113321,"uid":17809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T23:58:39.000Z","msg":"［愛你是我一生中理想］<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/55VXmMmgY9c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F55VXmMmgY9c&d=hObUr7UKzm7jHRUyz9oMSARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=ff4f294e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/55VXmMmgY9c</a><br />\n<br />\n是你賜　我生命愛一趟<br />\n迷糊夢裡你　來到推開一片窗<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">令我再有希望重拾情深一往<br />\n為何讓你　為何讓我受過傷的今天更傷</span><br />\n<br />\n＊<span style=\"color: red;\">無援地傷心一場　沒法知一些感情真相</span><br />\n餘情未了　卻不敢夢和想<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=hObUr7UKzm7jHRUyz9oMSARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=2a284d8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a>　魔鏡歌詞網 <br />\n無援地傷心一場　沒法可走出癡情方向<br />\n情懷如雨　永遠沒晴朗<br />\n(情懷如雨　怕再度回看)<br />\n<br />\n面對愛你不懂去收放<br />\n如能為你我　願賠上今天的創傷<br />\n令我再次失望　還是情深一往<br />\n愁時共你笑亦和你是我一生中的理想<br />\nRepeat＊＊＊<br />\n<br />\n聽到流馬尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ce7f97a16333c332f6b00399b423ed97a0c193","tid":1113321,"uid":219456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T00:00:21.000Z","msg":"放不低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為何永遠放不低 為何錯愛這一位<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nD歌詞真係好腰心腰肺"},{"pid":"1d48d9f37f5274c7714f1aff7c828da84baba6d5","tid":1113321,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T00:03:10.000Z","msg":"如何掉眼淚～"},{"pid":"abb1efa182eb8bab08294fbb8e64462160e22a6c","tid":1113321,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T00:07:35.000Z","msg":"感情線上"},{"pid":"475cfda93dd3d2a489591b0a4d544e16dd8aa186","tid":1113321,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d48d9f37f5274c7714f1aff7c828da84baba6d5","tid":1113321,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T00:03:10.000Z","msg":"如何掉眼淚～"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T00:08:09.000Z","msg":"欲哭找不到根據<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49cd6be1e807eba1f685b990b876fe9a1f7dde78","tid":1113321,"uid":17809,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T00:14:25.000Z","msg":"愛的輓歌<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/V_QR3a5MOuU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FV_QR3a5MOuU&d=hObUr7UKzm7jHRUyz9oMSARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=04c58950\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/V_QR3a5MOuU</a><br />\n<br />\n世間一切也無法去抵抗時日過　不管真心跟瞞騙亦同樣結果<br />\n來吧再一次被你欺騙未為過　明日我一個夜裡再哼這首輓歌<br />\n<br />\n想得很清楚　真愛難負荷　需要痛苦都太多<br />\n今宵可不可　無須要太清楚　只要剎那間結"},{"pid":"0b396d13817225e30cd9477ac05be9c4834303a9","tid":1113321,"uid":54852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T00:15:58.000Z","msg":"思念<br />\n承諾"},{"pid":"ca57bd1432986865b18d7dcad5d53bd08726cdf4","tid":1113321,"uid":88785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T01:01:49.000Z","msg":"一人十首就差唔多<br />\n<br />\n終生美麗<br />\n捨不得你<br />\n信者得愛<br />\n愛<br />\n一步一步愛<br />\n插曲<br />\n放不低<br />\n神奇女俠<br />\n愛是<br />\n交換溫柔"},{"pid":"45cb0800444f3d61169c90d4d6857fc65da5685a","tid":1113321,"uid":99610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T01:02:26.000Z","msg":"不拖不欠"},{"pid":"a13c0269eb4d729e857719853d1ea26278efb8f6","tid":1113321,"uid":74899,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T01:02:27.000Z","msg":"為何又是這樣錯"},{"pid":"ddfb0e307ebce85916118cca4968d8bb43626c39","tid":1113321,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB